msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Hey, watch where you're standin'!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "No, I...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "Hey, are you okay...!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "Can you move?\r\nCome on, answer me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "You should be checkin' on her instead..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Hm? <font_kind=yakuza_italic>Her</font_kind>...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "I'm all right, somehow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "What's going on here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Huh? Why am I over there?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "The hell's this shit?\r\nMy own body's... in front of me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "H-H-Huh? What's going on?\r\nHuh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Is this some kinda dream or somethin'...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "What is their problem?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "Lady Kazumiii! L-Lady Kazumi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "Let me get this straight. The shock from\r\nthe fall made you guys switch bodies?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "Yes. That's how it seems."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "It don't make any sense to me, either..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "So, you're Kazuo... and the one in that body is Kazumi.\r\nEven your names are confusing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Th-This is ridiculous.\r\nIt's not possible!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "Stay calm, Muranaka."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "You brat!\r\nHow dare you take that tone with me!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "You sure that's how you wanna talk to her?\r\nAin't she supposed to be your master?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Enough joking around, Lady Kazumi!\r\nWe need to get you to a hospital at once."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "It's fine, I ain't hurt or nothing.\r\nWe've got way bigger problems than that right now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "Your name's Kiryu-san, right? Sorry,\r\nbut mind not tellin' anyone about this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "Not that anyone's gonna believe you, anyways."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "Kazuo-kun... How are you so calm right now?\r\nThis is no time for joking around!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "Tch, enough of this charade..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Madam, I must insist that you\r\nreturn home!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "Fine, then Kazumi should come along..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Absolutely not!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "What...?\r\nBut Muranaka...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "I've said it enough times, thugs like him\r\nare not permitted at our residence."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "C'mon, you thick-headed butler.\r\nEven you gotta realize the mistake you're makin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "We've got to stick together or there's\r\nno way we'll figure out how to swap back..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "Now, enough of this strange behavior!\r\nWe're leaving, Madam!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "Kazumi, it'll be okay.\r\nI'll have someone come pick you up right away!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Yo... Kazuo, was it?\r\nEr, Kazumi for now, I guess."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "Is everything okay?\r\nIt sounded like you guys are in a complicated situation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Complicated wouldn't even cut it...\r\nAm I going to be in Kazuo-kun's body forever...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "Hey... Aw crap."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Crying isn't gonna fix anything..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "A guy's body isn't so bad, y'know.\r\nYou can piss standing up now, so that's something..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "Nah, I guess you'd rather look for a\r\nway to get your own body back, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "If there's any way I could help you out..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "Hm? Are you okay...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "No matter how hard you fall down the stairs,\r\npeople don't just swap bodies with each other, man!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "So this was all an act..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "Yep, you got it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "So you guys were lying about the\r\nbody swap thing the whole time?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "I guess if it were that easy, this sorta thing\r\nwould've happened to a lot of people by now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "I-I don't know w-what to tell you...\r\nbut it happened..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "But that means you and that girl are accomplices.\r\nWhy don't you drop the act already?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "So it was an act after all, huh?\r\nEverything including falling down the stairs..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "Yep, you got it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "If you need to cry,\r\nI'll lend you my shoulder to cry on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "Huh...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "Even though you're in a guy's body, you're a girl inside,\r\nright? I can't just leave a lady in distress."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "Come over here, Kazumi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "Hm? Are you okay...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "No matter how hard you fall down the stairs,\r\npeople don't just swap bodies with each other, man!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "So this was all an act..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "Yep, you got it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, was it?\r\nI feel bad about dragging you into all of this..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "But we have our own reasons for doing it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "And what reason is that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "Kazumi, the girl I claimed to switch places with...\r\nshe belongs to the Iwami family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "The Iwami family...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "Yeah, she's not part of the head family, but she's\r\npretty damn close. Basically... her family's loaded."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "No one would believe that Kazumi\r\nis dating a guy like me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I bet..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "For a girl as privileged as Kazumi, she's a good person.\r\nShe looks at who you are, not where you came from."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "And to get to the point...\r\nwe're in a serious relationship."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "But the people around us... especially that butler,\r\nMuranaka, are desperately trying to break us apart."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "He convinced her parents to send her away for school.\r\nIf that happens, we may never see each other again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "I see. So that's why you made up that act...\r\nYou guys didn't really have another choice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "If your daughter swaps bodies with someone, you can't\r\nexactly break 'em up until they swap back, y'know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "I doubt anyone would totally believe it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "That's the thing, they don't need to believe it 100%.\r\nYou just need them to believe it's possible."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "As long as we keep playing our parts, they should\r\nbelieve just enough to keep the two of us together."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "What a bizarre idea. Did you come up with it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "Nah, it's all her.\r\nShe got it from a movie or something."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "I see..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "Oh, hold up, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "It's Muranaka...\r\nKazumi probably sent him to pick me up..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "Nah... if that were the case,\r\nthere wouldn't be so many people."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "In any case, I'm gonna act like Kazumi again,\r\nso could you play along?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||||4"
msgid "Muranaka! You've come to pick me up, yes?\r\nWhere's Kazuo-kun?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "You have no business here.\r\nLeave us to our affairs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "And if I don't?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "If you stay, you'll suffer alongside him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "What is the meaning of this...?\r\nAnswer me, Muranaka!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "You shitty brat...\r\nHow long do you plan to keep up this act?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "No, this... isn't an act!\r\nI really swapped bodies with Kazuo-kun...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "Shut up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "121||||4"
msgid "How's that? If you don't want to get hurt,\r\nstop this disgusting act now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "No, Muranaka. It's really me, Kazumi.\r\nPlease believe me...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "Uh-huh, you just don't know when to give up...\r\nLet's see which gives out first, you or your lies..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "How's that!? Give up and apologize already!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||||4"
msgid "You're wrong!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "My name... is Kazumi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "130||||4"
msgid "You brat...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "131||||4"
msgid "That's enough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "I have nothing to do with any of this, but..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "I can't stand by and watch when\r\nsomeone lays their hands on a woman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "135||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||||4"
msgid "You're not from around here, are you?\r\nYou should have left while you had the chance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||||4"
msgid "I'll teach you what happens..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||||4"
msgid "When an outsider meddles in someone else's affairs!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||||4"
msgid "Kazuo-kun!? What happened to you!? And this is..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||||4"
msgid "I'm so sorry about Muranaka."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||||4"
msgid "Please forgive me, Kazuo-kun...\r\nI didn't think Muranaka could be so cruel..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "145||||4"
msgid "I'm fine, don't worry about me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "146||||4"
msgid "But Kiryu-san... why'd you step in to help me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "147||||4"
msgid "You knew that this was all an act. So why...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "148||||4"
msgid "No matter how much you got hurt,\r\nyou never stopped saying you were really Kazumi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "149||||4"
msgid "Maybe I just believed for a moment\r\nthat you really were Kazumi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "150||||4"
msgid "Sometimes, a lie that you risk your life for\r\ncan be true to someone... but only sometimes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "151||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "153||||4"
msgid "So? What are you guys gonna do now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "154||||4"
msgid "We're gonna continue this act, right...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "155||||4"
msgid "Yup... and if Muranaka attacks me again,\r\nI'll tell him that you have my back, Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156||||4"
msgid "Do what you want. I won't guarantee\r\nthat I'll actually come, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "157||||4"
msgid "But... I wonder how long\r\nwe'd have to keep this up..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "158||||4"
msgid "Yeah... I wouldn't mind keeping it going forever, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "159||||4"
msgid "Huh...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "160||||4"
msgid "If it's with you, I could lie forever.\r\nWe only need to be true to each other."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "161||||4"
msgid "Kazuo... kun..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "162||||4"
msgid "Can't you two do that in private?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "163||||4"
msgid "S-Sorry..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164||||4"
msgid "Well then... I'm good to go, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "165||||4"
msgid "Thank you so much, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "166||||4"
msgid "I'm very grateful. Thanks a lot!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "167||||4"
msgid "Quite the trouble I've caused."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168||||4"
msgid "Were you... watching this whole time?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "169||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I heard everything. It seems like\r\nthey've both strengthened their resolve."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "170||||4"
msgid "Did you know the whole time?\r\nWere you testing those two?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "171||||4"
msgid "What would you have done if I hadn't stopped you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "172||||4"
msgid "I wonder... But I assumed that you would."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "173||||4"
msgid "Sometimes you can tell what a person is\r\nthinking just by the look in their eyes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "174||||4"
msgid "Clever guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "175||||4"
msgid "I will continue to test them.\r\nIf you would like to interfere, please feel free."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "176||||4"
msgid "Nah... I'm sure they'll be fine,\r\nespecially with you on their side."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "177||||4"
msgid "Well, thank you. She's a handful...\r\nI guess new responsibilities are part of getting older."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "178||||4"
msgid "Yeah... I know what you mean."
msgstr ""

